// Tracked in git — the single source of truth for Lillist-macOS's build
// number. Incremented automatically by the Lillist-macOS scheme's Archive
// pre-action (Tools/Deploy/bump-build-number.sh). Commit after each
// archive so the counter never regresses.
//
// Dedicated macOS counter, separate from Apps/Config/BuildNumber.xcconfig
// (iOS). Before issue #55, the macOS app hardcoded CFBundleVersion to a
// stale literal (20260517) that never incremented, so Sparkle always
// reported "up to date" regardless of the appcast — this counter is what
// makes CFBundleVersion actually monotonic across macOS releases.
//
// Seeded at 49 so the first archive after this change bumps to 50 and
// ships CFBundleVersion = 50. NOTE (one-time transition): 50 is LOWER
// than the previously-shipped literal 20260517, so Sparkle's version
// comparator treats existing installs as already "newer" — those
// installs will not be auto-offered the first build-50+ release and need
// a one-time manual reinstall. Every build from 50 onward then
// auto-updates normally. See docs/engineering-notes.md and issue #55.
CURRENT_PROJECT_VERSION = 49
